      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you say my worth exists but it doesnt feel real. like if i just... stopped showing up. if i just stopped logging on and stopped being here. i dont think anyone would even notice for weeks. it feels like i dont leave any kind of footprint. like i'm just consuming space without actually being present in anyone's life.",
